    <div class="bg-brand-gray-200 p-6 border border-brand-gray-300 rounded-lg">
      <div class="md:text-left text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Risco Zero e Garantia Total</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-primary text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Eu confio tanto na metodologia <strong>BASE</strong> que ofereço uma garantia incondicional de <strong>7
